2.text: Angle a brush from your nose to your outer brow to find your end point.

3.text: Use eyeliner to make a dot just above your crease to mark the tip of your wing.
3.vid: /0/03/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 3 Version 5.360p.mp4

4.text: Draw a line connecting the dot to the outer corner of your eye.
4.vid: /d/df/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 4 Version 5.360p.mp4

5.text: Draw a line connecting the dot to the middle of your upper lash line.
5.vid: /7/7b/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 5 Version 5.360p.mp4

6.text: Fill in the outline you have made, if necessary.
6.vid: /6/6f/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 6 Version 5.360p.mp4

7.text: Clean up any mistakes with a pointed cotton swab.
7.vid: /c/c8/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 7 Version 5.360p.mp4

8.text: Draw a line to connect the inner corner of your eye with your cat eye.
8.vid: /8/88/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 8 Version 5.360p.mp4

9.text: Thicken the line as it gets closer toward the outer corner of your eye.
9.vid: /6/6d/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 9 Version 5.360p.mp4

10.vid: /8/8f/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 10 Version 4.360p.mp4

11.vid: /f/fc/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 11 Version 2.360p.mp4

12.text: Take a short piece of clear tape and tap it onto your hand.
12.vid: /6/68/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 12 Version 2.360p.mp4

13.text: Position the tape along the outer corner of your eye.

14.text: Draw a line from the inner corner of your eye to the outer corner.
14.vid: /a/a7/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 14 Version 2.360p.mp4

15.text: Use the tape as a guide to extend the line past the corner of your eye.
15.vid: /d/db/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 15 Version 2.360p.mp4

16.text: Remove the tape carefully and make any touch-ups, if necessary.
16.vid: /b/ba/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 16 Version 2.360p.mp4

17.text: Finish off with mascara or false lashes.
17.vid: /a/a5/Make Cat Eyes With Eyeliner Step 17 Version 2.360p.mp4
